metadata.name: Kitsch Kulture
metadata.description:
This is the genesis 1/1 piece by Ði ƵƵ y.

Hand drawn piece created to reflect some of the coolest elements of culture mixed with beautiful tropical/beach elements.  

The piece captures and represents elements of elements of culture in the 90's and early 2000's. The piece was created as a type of time machine to transport you back in time. 

I also wanted to create a beautiful piece with beautiful sup tropical plants and flowers. I wanted to create a sense of beauty and joy and love when looking at this beautiful creation.

This piece is in the DZY Collection.
